Package: ankiR
Title: Read 'Anki' Flashcard Databases
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Christos", "Longros", email = "chris.longros@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Read and analyze 'Anki' flashcard collection databases. Provides 
    functions to access notes, cards, decks, note types, and review logs from 
    'Anki' 'SQLite' databases with a tidy interface. Supports extraction of 
    'FSRS' (Free Spaced Repetition Scheduler) parameters including stability, 
    difficulty, and retrievability for advanced spaced repetition analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    DBI,
    RSQLite,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/chrislongros/ankiR
